<div id="about-panel" class="fixed inset-0 z-[200] hidden">
  <canvas id="about-canvas" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none" style="mix-blend-mode:screen"></canvas>
  <div id="about-overlay" class="absolute inset-0 bg-[rgba(7,1,15,0.92)] backdrop-blur-[4px]"></div>
  <div class="relative z-[201] w-full h-full opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-700 ease-out overflow-y-auto" id="about-content">
    <div class="min-h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-12 md:p-16 lg:p-24">
      <div class="w-full max-w-5xl">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-12">
          <h3 class="font-cinzel text-[14px] text-[#d688ff] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase flex items-center gap-[10px]">
            <span class="block w-5 h-[0.5px] bg-[#c44bff] opacity-50"></span>
            About Me
          </h3>
          <button id="about-close" class="text-[#9b72c0] text-[22px] cursor-pointer hover:text-[#ff85c0] transition-colors border-none bg-transparent">
            <i class="ti ti-x"></i>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-12 items-start">
          <div class="w-full aspect-[3/4] rounded-[2px] overflow-hidden border border-[rgba(255,45,138,0.15)]">
            <img src="/about-photo.jpg" alt="Ailen Colazo" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
            <h1 class="font-cinzel text-[36px] md:text-[42px] font-semibold text-[#f8eaff] leading-[1.1] tracking-[0.04em]">
              Ailen Colazo
              <span class="block text-[16px] text-[#ff85c0] font-normal font-grotesk tracking-[0.15em] mt-2">3D Artist &amp; Game Developer</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-[#c9a8e8] leading-[1.9] font-light">
              Born in Caleta Olivia, Santa Cruz, Patagonia, Argentina. Passionate about world-building, character creation, and interactive experiences.
              Specialized in 3D modeling, sculpting, texturing, lighting, and game development with Unreal Engine 5.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-[#c9a8e8] leading-[1.9] font-light">
              Currently developing <span class="text-[#ff85c0] font-medium">Ritual Of Awakening</span>, a third-person action-adventure game built from scratch in UE5.
              Every asset, character, and environment is crafted with attention to detail and narrative depth.
